":"3848ceb02b"},{"id":"b3f45c34f4","type":"paragraph","text":"毛远新","index":41,"publicationId":"aee1f9e8-a37b-4f7a-8a7c-bcea461eb5fc","articleId":"3848ceb02b"},{"id":"b48ad7e4c7","type":"paragraph","text":"丁盛","index":21,"publicationId":"aee1f9e8-a37b-4f7a-8a7c-bcea461eb5fc","articleId":"3848ceb02b"},{"id":"bbf024238b","type":"paragraph","text":"刘大杰","index":54,"publicationId":"aee1f9e8-a37b-4f7a-8a7c-bcea461eb5fc","articleId":"3848ceb02b"},{"id":"c5fdbf75a6","type":"paragraph","text":"朱永嘉","index":60,"publicationId":"aee1f9e8-a37b-4f7a-8a7c-bcea461eb5fc","articleId":"3848ceb02b"},{"id":"c7c1abd3fd","type":"paragraph","text":"龙太忠","index":38,"publicationId":"aee1f9e8-a37b-4f7a-8a7c-bcea461eb5fc","articleId":"3848ceb02b"},{"id":"c883fd6542","type":"paragraph","text":"朱蕴山","index":62,"publicationId":"aee1f9e8-a37b-4f7a-8a7c-bcea461eb5fc","articleId":"3848ceb02b"},{"id":"d3f7e80b03","type":"paragraph","text":"主席团和秘书长名单主席团（共二百一十八名，按姓氏笔划为序）","index":20,"publicationId":"aee1f9e8-a37b-4f7a-8a7c-bcea461eb5fc","articleId":"3848ceb02b"},{"id":"d4a2d47c68","type":"paragraph","text":"王必成王芸生","index":28,"publicationId":"aee1f9e8-a37b-4f7a-8a7c-bcea461eb5fc","articleId":"3848ceb02b"},{"id":"d7a394b234","type":"paragraph","text":"大会根据中共十届二中全会提出的候选人名单，经过认真讨论，用无记名投票方式，选出了第四届全国人民代表大会常务委员会委员长，副委员长，委员，任命了国务院总理、副总理、各部部长、各委员会主任。","index":13,"publicationId":"aee1f9e8-a37b-4f7a-8a7c-bcea461eb5fc","articleId":"3848ceb02b"},{"id":"d82435ce63","type":"paragraph","text":"马惠敏（女）","index":25,"publicationId":"aee1f9e8-a37b-4f7a-8a7c-bcea461eb5fc","articleId":"3848ceb02b"},{"id":"dd263b40bd","type":"paragraph","text":"王克强","index":29,"publicationId":"aee1f9e8-a37b-4f7a-8a7c-bcea461eb5fc","articleId":"3848ceb02b"},{"id":"e0abb1095d","type":"paragraph","text":"刘大年","index":53,"publicationId":"aee1f9e8-a37b-4f7a-8a7c-bcea461eb5fc","articleId":"3848ceb02b"},{"id":"e581043f2b","type":"paragraph","text":"马正寿马宁王大任","index":26,"publicationId":"aee1f9e8-a37b-4f7a-8a7c-bcea461eb5fc","articleId":"3848ceb02b"},{"id":"e7f31f7d23","type":"paragraph","text":"一月十七日，全体代表一致通过了修政后的《中华人民共和国宪法》和张春桥同志所作的《关于修改宪法的报告》，一致通过了关于政府工作报告的快议，批准了周恩来总理所作的《政府工作报告》。代表们为完成了具有历史意义的光荣任务而响起了经久不息的掌声。","index":12,"publicationId":"aee1f9e8-a37b-4f7a-8a7c-bcea461eb5fc","articleId":"3848ceb02b"},{"id":"e98bfc869c","type":"paragraph","text":"中华人民共和国第四届全国人民代表大会第一次会议于一九七五年一月十三日至十七日在北京隆重举行。","index":3,"publicationId":"aee1f9e8-a37b-4f7a-8a7c-bcea461eb5fc","articleId":"3848ceb02b"},{"id":"efcfe731ce","type":"paragraph","text":"乌云其其格（女）","index":42,"publicationId":"aee1f9e8-a37b-4f7a-8a7c-bcea461eb5fc","articleId":"3848ceb02b"},{"id":"f08d2edaaa","type":"paragraph","text":"当宣布选举结果和任命名单时，全场又一次响起了长时间的热烈的掌声。","index":14,"publicationId":"aee1f9e8-a37b-4f7a-8a7c-bcea461eb5fc","articleId":"3848ceb02b"},{"id":"f28067e425","type":"paragraph","text":"昌玉兰（女）","index":51,"publicationId":"aee1f9e8-a37b-4f7a-8a7c-bcea461eb5fc","articleId":"3848ceb02b"},{"id":"fb68caede2","type":"paragraph","text":"在主席台前列就座的还有：周恩来、王洪文、叶剑英、邓小平、张春桥、江青、许世友、华国锋、陈永贵、陈锅联、李先念、李德生、姚文元、吴桂贤、苏振华、倪志福。朱德委员长宣布大会开幕，全体代表热烈鼓掌。乐队奏国歌。","index":6,"publicationId":"aee1f9e8-a37b-4f7a-8a7c-bcea461eb5fc","articleId":"3848ceb02b"},{"id":"fdc0022e17","type":"paragraph","text":"大会的议程是：一、修改先法；二、政府工作报告；三，选举和任命国家领导工作人员。","index":4,"publicationId":"aee1f9e8-a37b-4f7a-8a7c-bcea461eb5fc","articleId":"3848ceb02b"},{"id":"fee68e32e2","type":"paragraph","text":"朱光亚","index":61,"publicationId":"aee1f9e8-a37b-4f7a-8a7c-bcea461eb5fc","articleId":"3848ceb02b"}],"page":{"id":"03db9ad611","publicationId":"aee1f9e8-a37b-4f7a-8a7c-bcea461eb5fc","articleId":"3848ceb02b","start":31,"end":34}}}},"__N_SSG":true}